@node ENEMIES "Enemies"
Some of the computer opponents (from the manual):-

GHOST    -=-  Can go through walls. IQ significance: for evasive purposes.

RUNNER   -=-  Fast & strong, no special abilities. IQ significance: as above

MINER    -=-  Lays mines. IQ significance: for evasive puposes and
              frequency of mines.

BUILDER  -=-  Builds blocks. IQ significance: for evasive purposes and
              frequency of walls

FLASH    -=-  Really fast. On contact will place Bomb's all around its
              enemy i.e. you and your robots. IQ significance: for evasive
              purposes. (We call it Psycho here of obvious reasons)


