@node OTHERS "Other Information..."

Other information:-


The demo's 4 levels are not 4 levels in a row that increase in
difficulty slowly - They must be 4 levels that are from various stages in
the game i.e. level 10, 20, 30, 40 !!! with the computer IQ of 3 ??? Who
knows!!

I have (finally) got in touch with Kingsoft who have said they don't mind
this providing I only make the DEMO available (which is obvious really!)
so this is all legal (not that it wasn't anyway).


